1. Moj brat je *lud* za automobilima. (My brother is crazy about cars.)
2. Jučerašnja *ludost* me je skupo koštala. (Yesterday's madness cost me dearly.)
3. Njegova *ludost* za sportom je neograničena. (His madness for sports is limitless.)
4. Upuštanje u takve *ludosti* bi bilo vrlo opasno. (Engaging in such madness would be very dangerous.)
5. Našao sam se u situaciji da moram da radim sa *ludim* čovekom. (I found myself in a situation where I had to work with a crazy person.)
6. *Ludilo* se oduvek smatralo znakom genijalnosti. (Madness has always been considered a sign of genius.)
7. Njegova *ludost* je prešla sve granice. (His madness has crossed all boundaries.)
8. U poslednje vreme, sve više ljudi se žali na *ludost* omladine. (Lately, more and more people are complaining about the madness of youth.)
9. Izgleda da je svet u potpunom *ludilu*. (It seems that the world is in complete madness.)
10. Čini se da *ludost* ima svoje granice, ali glupost nema. (It seems that madness has its limits, but stupidity does not.)